WEBVTT

00:00.106 --> 00:01.675
Previously on "Heartland"...

00:01.752 --> 00:04.127
The reason I invited Mitchfor dinner
yesterday

00:04.243 --> 00:07.430
was that we wanted
to tell everyone about us.

00:07.916 --> 00:09.551
About our relationship.

00:09.615 --> 00:11.451
Maybe luch at Maggies tomorrow?

00:11.554 --> 00:13.264
- You're sure?
- Positive.

00:13.791 --> 00:15.533
Hanging out, having lunch.

00:15.881 --> 00:17.675
That's what friends do, right?

00:19.659 --> 00:20.831
W-we're going back.

00:20.905 --> 00:23.059
Bob? What's going on? Where is Ty?

00:24.104 --> 00:27.186
Well, Ty is a little sick
and he missed his flight.

00:27.977 --> 00:29.413
I need to see him.

00:29.539 --> 00:31.682
And I'll have him on a
plane as soon as I can.

00:32.464 --> 00:33.973
I promise.

00:35.000 --> 00:41.074
